profile:
Professional Home Audio/Video & Network Services
 
We are a fully insured and licensed company serving Calgary and all surrounding areas.  We offer everything from a basic TV wall mount to whole-home networked audio, video and automation systems.  Best prices and top notch service.
 
Services Include:
Basic and custom TV wall mounting
Multi-room Audio Systems
Audiophile 2-channel Audio Systems
Home Theatre Setup and Troubleshooting
Networking and WiFi boosters
Pre-wire and retrofit
Universal Remote Control Programming
Home Automation and Control Systems
LED Lighting
 
We are an authorized dealer of many top brands including Anthem, Martin Logan, Cambridge Audio, RBH, Marantz, Panasonic Projectors, Epson Projectors and Elunevision Screens.
